  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nOur BLS library has upgrade to [`v0.4.1`](https://github.com/sigp/signature-schemes/releases/tag/0.4.1) to include a `domain` parameter.\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nThere is no domain information included on signatures.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nDomains should be added to all signing and verification.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\n1. Bump the `Cargo.toml` version to `v0.4.1`\r\n2. Ensure all existing signatures are updated to include the correct domain.\r\n",
